quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,So I do not swear/make oath with what you see
  69,39,And what you do not see
  69,40,That it truly is an honoured/noble messenger`s word/saying (E)
  69,41,"And it is not with a poet`s word/saying , little (is) what you believe"
  69,42,"And nor with a fortune teller`s/altar priests word/saying , little (is) what you mention/remember"
  69,43,Descent from the creations all together`s/(universe`s) Lord
  69,44,And if (the messenger) made false statements on Us (on Our behalf) some (of) the sayings/beliefs
  69,45,We would have punished/taken from him by the right (hand)
  69,46,Then We would have severed/cut off from him the aorta/heart`s main artery
  69,47,So (there) is not from anyone from you preventing/hindering from (for) him
  69,48,And that it truly is a reminder for the fearing and obeying
  69,49,"And We (E), We know (E) that (E) from you (are) liars/deniers/falsifiers"
  69,50,"And that it truly is grief/sadness (E) , on the disbelievers"
  69,51,And that it truly is true/real (E) the assurance/certainty
  69,52,So praise/glorify with your Lord`s name the great